  <!-- EN: Burya -->
  <VVE_Burya_Blueprint.label>暴风火箭炮</VVE_Burya_Blueprint.label>
  <!-- EN: A dedicated multiple launch rocket system platform, the Burya is a long-range siege and area denial weapon that can be operated by a two-man crew for faster loading speeds. Capable of firing continuous volleys of long range missiles, Burya can blanket whole areas in anti-infantry rocket explosions.\n\nSlow-moving and vulnerable to enemy fire, Burya needs to deploy before it can open fire, which may leave it stranded in enemy territory.\n\n<color=#bb8f04>Crew:</color> Driver x1, Gunner x2\n<color=#bb8f04>Fuel type:</color> Chemfuel -->
  <VVE_Burya_Blueprint.description>暴风是专业的多管火箭发射平台，专用于在远距离上对指定区域里的工事进行打击，分配二人炮组可以加快装弹速度。可以持续发射一波又一波的长程火箭弹，将目标区域整个覆盖在反步兵火箭的爆炸下。\n\n暴风火箭炮速度缓慢，装甲薄弱，并且需要在部署后才能射击，务必要做好掩护工作。\n\n&lt;color=#bb8f04&gt;乘员：&lt;/color&gt;驾驶员 x1 炮手 x2\n&lt;color=#bb8f04&gt;动力：&lt;/color&gt;化合燃料</VVE_Burya_Blueprint.description>
  
</LanguageData>